    <item>
      <title>A House That Appears Empty from the Outside</title>
      <link>https://www.musnotes.my.id/en/digital-garden/silva-nigra/art-resonance/sebuah_rumah_/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 May 2026 22:06:00 +0700</pubDate>
      <guid>https://www.musnotes.my.id/en/digital-garden/silva-nigra/art-resonance/sebuah_rumah_/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Listening to: Clara Schumann — Nocturne Op. 6 No. 2 (1827 Stein piano)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&#34;position: relative; padding-bottom: 56.25%; height: 0; overflow: hidden;&#34;&gt;
      &lt;iframe allow=&#34;accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share; fullscreen&#34; loading=&#34;eager&#34; referrerpolicy=&#34;strict-origin-when-cross-origin&#34; src=&#34;https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZEkD2ZCe9eE?autoplay=0&amp;amp;controls=1&amp;amp;end=0&amp;amp;loop=0&amp;amp;mute=0&amp;amp;start=0&#34; style=&#34;position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%; border:0;&#34; title=&#34;YouTube video&#34;&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div class=&#34;mus-divider&#34; aria-hidden=&#34;true&#34;&gt;&lt;svg viewBox=&#34;0 0 100 100&#34; class=&#34;mus-symbol&#34; xmlns=&#34;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#34;&gt;
  &lt;circle cx=&#34;50&#34; cy=&#34;50&#34; r=&#34;8&#34; fill=&#34;currentColor&#34;/&gt;
  &lt;ellipse cx=&#34;50&#34; cy=&#34;50&#34; rx=&#34;40&#34; ry=&#34;25&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; transform=&#34;rotate(-15 50 50)&#34;/&gt;
  &lt;ellipse cx=&#34;50&#34; cy=&#34;50&#34; rx=&#34;30&#34; ry=&#34;45&#34; fill=&#34;none&#34; stroke=&#34;currentColor&#34; stroke-width=&#34;2&#34; transform=&#34;rotate(60 50 50)&#34;/&gt;
&lt;/svg&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I listened to it through my earbuds with eyes closed, letting every detail of the sound felt in its entirety. This music is profoundly soothing, slowly carrying me to another world—to a house that appeared empty from the outside. Yet inside, I saw a young girl playing a bell. Suddenly, it was as if a faint, illusory sound of a bell seeped into and merged with the music itself.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
